---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Simon Rogers - 30 years of championship-winning suspension expertise. Founder of RaceShocks.UK, Meteor Motorsport, and CORE Suspension.">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
      <h1>About <span class="text-green">Simon</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">30+ years of expertise, from hillclimb wins to founding industry-leading brands.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Section -->
  <section class="bio-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="bio-grid">
        <div class="bio-image">
          <div class="image-frame">
            <img src="/images/Simon 2019 Champion.jpg" alt="Simon Rogers" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bio-content">
          <h2>The Story</h2>
          <p>Simon Rogers has been immersed in motorsport for over three decades. What started as a passion for making cars go faster evolved into a career defining the standards for lightweight sports car suspension worldwide.</p>
          
          <p>A racer himself, Simon understands what drivers need because he's been there – pushing cars to their limits on track, hillclimb, and road. His Caterham 7 has seen victory at venues like Curborough, Gurston Down and Prescott.  Curborough being of particular importance where he has the 3 fastest time of any car other than a single seat race car with aero.</p>
          
          <p>This hands-on experience informs everything we do at Too Fast To Race. When you talk to us about suspension setup, you're talking to someone who's felt the difference a shim stack change makes through a high-speed or low-speed corner.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Track Record -->
  <section class="track-record">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
        <h2>Track Record</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">Founded</span>
            <h3>RS Automotive Engineering</h3>
            <p>Trading as RaceShocks.UK and MeteorMotorsport.com – becoming a leading UK suspension specialist for lightweight sports cars.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">Partnership</span>
            <h3>CORE Suspension</h3>
            <p>Partnered with TracTive Suspension BV (Netherlands) to create CORE Suspension – the first brand focused entirely on lightweight sports cars. TracTive supplies BMW, Dallara, Pagani, and RUF.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">Competition</span>
            <h3>Hillclimb Success</h3>
            <p>Multiple championship wins, class victories and record times at UK hillclimb & speed venues – consistently finishing on the podium in Caterham 7.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker"></div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="timeline-date">Today</span>
            <h3>Too Fast To Race</h3>
            <p>S Rogers Engineering Ltd – returning to the core passion: hands-on suspension development, Caterham builds, and bespoke engineering projects in rural Wales.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Expertise -->
  <section class="expertise">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="expertise-grid">
        <div class="expertise-content">
          <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
          <h2>Expertise</h2>
          <p>Working across the full spectrum of performance suspension – from road-focused comfort to all-out race specification:</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="expertise-list">
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h4>Damper Technology</h4>
            <p>Expert knowledge of Penske, Nitron, Ohlins, Quantum, and TracTive damper systems. Custom valving for any application.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h4>Lightweight Sports Cars</h4>
            <p>Specialist focus on Caterham, Lotus, Ariel, TVR, and Alpine. These cars demand suspension that understands their unique dynamics.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h4>Testing & Development</h4>
            <p>Professional dyno testing, on-car data acquisition, and iterative development. We measure, test, and refine until it's right.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="expertise-item">
            <h4>Chassis Setup</h4>
            <p>Complete vehicle dynamics – corner weighting, geometry optimisation, spring selection, and ride height calibration.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote -->
  <section class="quote-section">
    <div class="container">
      <blockquote>
        <p>"IWhilst we have worked with many brands of suspension we choose to partner with those who build with quality.  What we have learnt over the many years of service and testing is that understanding what a change on a certain type of damper actually does is vital to on track performance and adjustment.  We dont guess. We measure test and then do the maths. Make the relevant changes and then test again. "</p>
        <cite>– Simon Rogers</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Let's Talk Suspension</h2>
        <p>Whether you're looking for setup advice, custom valving, or a complete build – get in touch.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Simon</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Bio Section */
  .bio-section {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .bio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .bio-image .image-frame {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .bio-image .image-frame::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: -10px;
    border: 2px solid var(--tftr-green);
    transform: translate(-15px, -15px);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .bio-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .bio-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .bio-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Track Record / Timeline */
  .track-record {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    padding-left: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--tftr-green), rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.2));
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: calc(-1 * var(--space-lg) - 6px);
    top: 0;
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    background: var(--tftr-green);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .timeline-date {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .timeline-content h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  /* Expertise */
  .expertise {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .expertise-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .expertise-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .expertise-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .expertise-item {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--tftr-green);
  }

  .expertise-item h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .expertise-item p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Quote Section */
  .quote-section {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  blockquote p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--tftr-white);
    max-width: none;
  }

  blockquote cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tftr-green-dark), var(--tftr-green));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: var(--space-sm) auto var(--space-md);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .bio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .bio-image {
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .expertise-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .expertise-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
